ricks.com/2018_WATCH_LIST.pdf|date=August 14, 2018|accessdate=August 16, 2018}}</ref>\n|Breckyn Hager\n|DE\n|SR\n|-\n|[[Earl Campbell Tyler Rose Award]]<ref>{{cite web|title=2018 Nominations The Earl Campbell Tyler Rose Award|url=http://www.earlcampbellaward.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/2018-Nominations-The-Earl-Campbell-Tyler-Rose-Award.pdf|date=August 16, 2018|accessdate=August 17, 2018}}</ref>\n|Collin Johnson\n|WR\n|JR\n|}\n\n===Big 12 media poll===\nThe Big 12 media poll was released on July 12, 2018 with the Longhorns predicted to finish in fourth place.<ref>http://www.big12sports.com/ViewArticle.dbml?DB_OEM_ID=10410&ATCLID=211734508</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n|align=\"center\" Colspan=\"3\" |'''Media poll'''\n|- align=\"center\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Texas Longhorns|Predicted finish|Team|Votes (1st place)}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 1 || Oklahoma || 509 (46)\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 2 || West Virginia || 432 (2)\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 3 || TCU || 390 (1)\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 4 || '''Texas''' || 370 (1)\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 5 || Oklahoma State || 300\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 6 || Kansas State || 283 (2)\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 7 || Iowa State || 250\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 8 || Texas Tech || 149\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 9 || Baylor || 125\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 10 || Kansas || 52\n|}\n\n==Schedule==\n{{CFB schedule\n| time = y \n| tv = y\n| attend = y \n| rank = y\n| opprank = y\n| rankyear = 2018\n| rankdivision = NCAA Division I FBS\n| poll = AP\n| timezone = Central\n\n| September 1 | 11:00 a.m. |v| [[2018 Maryland Terrapins football team|Maryland]]<ncg> | 23 | [[FedExField]] | [[Landover, Maryland|Landover, MD]] | [[Fox College Football|FS1]]  | L 29\u201334 | 47,641\n| September 8 | 7:00 p.m. || [[2018 Tulsa Golden Hurricane football team|Tulsa]]<ncg> | | [[Darrell K Royal\u2013Texas Memorial Stadium]] | [[Austin, Texas|Austin, TX]] | [[Longhorn Network|LHN]]  | W 28\u201321 | 90,563\n| September 15 | 7:00 p.m.  |  |